<h2>Watch If You Liked…</h2>
<p><em>Disclosure Day</em> keeping you up at 2 AM? Go straight to <em>Arrival</em>. Or <em>Annihilation</em>, if you want the same spiral but darker and weirder (which you do). More of a <em>Killer Whale</em> person? <em>Crawl</em> and <em>The Shallows</em> are right there, and they will not be gentle with you either.</p>

